# LevelUp App — Cursor Rules

## Project Overview
React Native mobile app using Expo Router + TypeScript + Supabase.
Converts LinkedIn and Google Fit data into an RPG character system.
Users get a character with 6 stats, a class, and a level that reflects their real life.

## Tech Stack
- Expo SDK 55 with Expo Router (file-based routing)
- TypeScript strict mode
- Supabase (auth, postgres database)
- NativeWind v4 NOT USED — use StyleSheet.create only
- React Query (TanStack v5) for data fetching
- expo-secure-store for token storage

