  body: 'Inter_400Regular'
  bodyBold: 'Inter_700Bold'

Spacing: xs=4, sm=8, md=16, lg=24, xl=32, xxl=48
Border radius: sm=6, md=10, lg=16, full=999

Import colors/fonts/spacing like this:
  import { COLORS, FONTS, SPACING, BORDER_RADIUS } from '../../constants/theme'
  import { STAT_COLORS } from '../../constants/theme'

## TypeScript Types (already defined in types/index.ts)
- StatName: 'STR' | 'INT' | 'WIS' | 'VIT' | 'CHA' | 'AGI'
- Tier: 'Basic' | 'Intermediate'
- ClassArchetype: 'Grinder' | 'Ironclad' | 'Ascendant' | 'Tactician' | 'Drifter' | 'Sage'
- EventType: 'career' | 'fitness'
- EducationLevel: 'highschool' | 'bachelors' | 'masters' | 'phd'
- Character: { id, userId, class, tier, level, totalXp, careerXp, fitnessXp, createdAt, updatedAt }
- Stat: { id, characterId, statName, baseScore, activeScore, lastUpdated }
- XPEvent: { id, userId, eventType, eventName, xpGained, statAffected, statDelta, createdAt }
- ManualEntryData: { avgDailySteps, workoutDaysPerWeek, avgSleepHours, yearsExperience, educationLevel, industryCount, certCount, endorsedSkills, connections, recommendations, careerSwitches }

## Supabase Tables
- profiles (id, username, created_at)
- characters (id, user_id, class, tier, level, total_xp, career_xp, fitness_xp, created_at, updated_at)
- stats (id, character_id, stat_name, base_score, active_score, last_updated)
- xp_events (id, user_id, event_type, event_name, xp_gained, stat_affected, stat_delta, created_at)
- connected_accounts (id, user_id, provider, access_token, refresh_token, expires_at, created_at)
- feedback (id, user_id, liked, confusing, would_use, created_at)

## Stat Logic
- Total stat = (base * 0.7) + (active * 0.3), capped at 100
- Base only moves up (high watermark), never decreases
- WIS and INT never decay
- VIT, STR, AGI active score decays after 30 days inactivity

## XP Logic
- Level threshold = 1000 * (level ^ 1.5)
- Career XP from LinkedIn events
- Fitness XP from Google Fit / manual events
- XP weights: promotion=500, certification=150, new_skill=30,
  workout_session=50, streak_7day=200, steps_goal=20,
  new_connection=15, career_switch=300

## Class System
6 archetypes with XP multipliers:
- Grinder: primary WIS+INT (x1.5), secondary CHA+AGI (x1.2)
- Ironclad: primary STR+VIT (x1.5), secondary AGI (x1.2)
- Ascendant: all equal (x1.1), gets synergy bonus
- Tactician: primary INT+CHA (x1.5), secondary WIS (x1.2)
- Drifter: primary AGI (x1.5), secondary CHA+VIT (x1.2)
- Sage: primary WIS+INT (x1.5), secondary VIT (x1.2)

Class names lookup:
- Grinder Basic="The Striver", Intermediate="The Relentless"
- Ironclad Basic="The Enduring", Intermediate="The Unbroken"
- Ascendant Basic="The Balanced", Intermediate="The Aligned"
- Tactician Basic="The Shrewd", Intermediate="The Architect"
- Drifter Basic="The Wanderer", Intermediate="The Untethered"
- Sage Basic="The Knowing", Intermediate="The Deepened"

## Code Rules — ALWAYS FOLLOW THESE
1. Use StyleSheet.create for ALL styling — no inline styles except position/flex overrides
2. Import types from ../../types or ../types depending on depth
3. Import constants from ../../constants/theme
4. All Supabase calls go through hooks in /hooks — never call supabase directly in screens
5. All business logic stays in /utils — never in components or screens
6. Always handle loading state with ActivityIndicator in gold color
7. Always handle error state with red error text
8. No hardcoded colors — always use COLORS.x
9. No hardcoded font names — always use FONTS.x
10. No any types — use proper TypeScript types
11. Navigation uses useRouter from expo-router
12. Auth state comes from useAuth hook
13. Character data comes from useCharacter(user?.id) hook
14. XP events come from useXPEvents(user?.id) hook

## Aesthetic
- Dark anime/manga style
- Gold accents throughout
- Bangers font for all headings, level numbers, class names, button text
- Inter for all body text, labels, descriptions
- Manga speed lines for decorative backgrounds (thin Views rotated)
- Character card has gold border + gold glow shadow
- Buttons: gold filled (primary), gold outline (secondary)
- All screens dark background #0D0D0D

